msgid "Included postcodes"
msgstr ""

#: includes/class-mfb-shipping-method.php:403
msgid ""
"Limits the service only to these postcodes. One rule per line (or same line "
"and separated by a comma), using the following format: XX-YYYYY (XX = alpha2 "
"country code, YYYYY = full postcode or prefix). Whitespaces will be ignored. "
"You can also specify country codes without postcodes (just \"XX\"). Leave "
"blank to apply no limitation."
msgstr ""

#: includes/class-mfb-shipping-method.php:409
msgid "Excluded postcodes"
msgstr ""

#: includes/class-mfb-shipping-method.php:411
msgid ""
